00:59:25,401 --> 00:59:26,544
Scott: And I had a whole bag of stuff.

866
00:59:26,925 --> 00:59:31,880
Scott: And the way to prevent that is, like I said, A, give people less stuff, right?

867
00:59:32,280 --> 00:59:36,013
Scott: That way it's like if they already have a cable, then they can use it again.

868
00:59:36,073 --> 00:59:37,960
Scott: They don't, you know, got an iPhone, you got a new iPhone.

869
00:59:38,120 --> 00:59:39,363
Scott: You still got cables lying around.

