01:01:04,005 --> 01:01:05,260
Scott: I didn't need, I had like separate.

900
01:01:05,860 --> 01:01:14,840
Rym: You got to have, generally a good idea is have at most of that kind of thing, the one extra that you use, like, oh, hey, I bought a new computer and I need to be able to set it up or something.

