01:01:15,182 --> 01:01:16,980
Rym: And then the backup, just in case.

902
01:01:17,060 --> 01:01:17,201
Scott: Yeah.

903
01:01:17,421 --> 01:01:22,520
Scott: I mean, if I buy a new computer, it's going to come with a power supply and the power supply is going to have another one of those fucking cables.

904
01:01:22,980 --> 01:01:23,281
Scott: Right.

905
01:01:23,562 --> 01:01:25,388
Scott: And it's like, I don't need another one of those.

