01:01:25,408 --> 01:01:26,974
Scott: You just give me the power supply only.

907
01:01:26,994 --> 01:01:28,800
Scott: I don't even need the internal cables.

908
01:01:28,920 --> 01:01:31,057
Scott: My old power supply had a bag of them.

909
01:01:31,299 --> 01:01:31,480
Scott: Right.

910
01:01:33,141 --> 01:01:33,341
Rym: Yeah.

911
01:01:33,381 --> 01:01:40,660
Rym: In fact, internal power supplies, the fact that there are modular ones, we should mandate by law that power supplies like that should be modular and standardized.

912
01:01:41,001 --> 01:01:44,190
Rym: That way I don't even need to get more like that rat's nest of cables.

913
01:01:44,431 --> 01:01:47,700
Rym: I only use three of them, two for the video card, one for the motherboard anyway.

914
01:01:47,800 --> 01:01:48,661
Rym: Yep.

