968
01:05:21,091 --> 01:05:22,192
Rym: You don't check it.

969
01:05:22,212 --> 01:05:23,513
Rym: You don't get the plastic silverware.

970
01:05:23,733 --> 01:05:26,196
Rym: You should have to say, I want all the cables.

971
01:05:26,936 --> 01:05:29,358
